
Library Manager

A web-based personal library management system that allows users to catalog books, store their physical locations, and manage their collection through a clean and intuitive interface. The application supports both manual book entry and image-based metadata extraction with ISBN lookup via Google Books API.

Live Demo:  
https://library-manager-production-c8f4.up.railway.app

Features

- Add books with title, author, genre, and physical location
- Mandatory location tracking (shelf, room, etc.)
- Search books by title
- Sort library alphabetically by title
- Remove books from the collection
- Upload book images for metadata extraction
- ISBN detection using Google Books API
- Clean, minimal, user-friendly UI
- Deployed on Railway (cloud hosted)

